  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个监控总线包处理模块，主要处理64位的监控包。入口是一个叫mon_in的端口，包含valid信号和packet数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mon_in",
        "monbus_valid",
        "monbus_packet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，mon_in是入口。那这个包进来之后第一步做什么？是直接过滤还是先解析？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mon_in",
        "PARSE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要先做一个Packet Parser，把包里的pkt_type、protocol和event_code解析出来。这个解析器我命名为PARSE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE",
        "pkt_type",
        "protocol",
        "event_code"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在Monitor Bus Input子图里把mon_in连接到PARSE，标注上解析的字段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MON_IN",
        "PARSE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "解析完之后进入Per-Protocol Filtering阶段。这里需要一个Filter Logic，根据配置寄存器来决定哪些包可以通过。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FILTER",
        "Per-Protocol Filtering"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Filter Logic的输入有哪些？除了PARSE的输出，还有哪些配置信号？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FILTER",
        "PARSE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有三个配置掩码：AXI_MASK用于AXI包过滤，包含cfg_axi_pkt_mask和cfg_axi_err_select；AXIS_MASK用于AXIS相关过滤；还有CORE_MASK用于核心级别的过滤。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI_MASK",
        "cfg_axi_pkt_mask",
        "cfg_axi_err_select",
        "AXIS_MASK",
        "cfg_axis_*_mask",
        "CORE_MASK",
        "cfg_core_*_mask"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加这三个配置掩码节点，都指向FILTER。AXI_MASK、AXIS_MASK、CORE_MASK作为FILTER的输入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI_MASK",
        "AXIS_MASK",
        "CORE_MASK",
        "FILTER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "FILTER之后需要做一个路由决策。首先判断是否要丢弃这个包，用一个Drop?的决策节点，检查pkt_mask位是否被设置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DROP",
        "pkt_mask"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Drop?节点，如果是Yes就走丢弃路径，No就继续处理对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DROP",
        "DISCARD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Yes走DISCARD节点，直接丢弃包。No的话进入ERR_CHK，判断是否是错误选择。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DROP",
        "DISCARD",
        "ERR_CHK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Routing Decision子图里，FILTER连到DROP，DROP分两支：Yes到DISCARD，No到ERR_CHK。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FILTER",
        "DROP",
        "DISCARD",
        "ERR_CHK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ERR_CHK也是决策点，Yes表示这是错误包，走ERR_PATH；No就是正常写包，走WR_PATH。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ERR_CHK",
        "ERR_PATH",
        "WR_PATH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加ERR_PATH和WR_PATH两个分支。ERR_CHK的Yes连到ERR_PATH，No连到WR_PATH。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ERR_CHK",
        "ERR_PATH",
        "WR_PATH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
